### projectItems.updateCost [POST /projectItems.updateCost]

Update a project item's internal cost.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes (object)
        + id: `cfb4146d-06be-41f1-bb39-aa3c929c71dc` (string, required)
        + internal_cost_per_unit (Money, required, nullable)

+ Response 204 (application/json;charset=utf-8)

### projectItems.updateInternalHourlyCost [POST /projectItems.updateInternalHourlyCost]

Updates the internal hourly cost for a participant, for a specific project or all projects. Only account administrators have access to this endpoint.
This does not update the global internal rate of the employee. See `users.update`.

+ Request (application/json;charset=utf-8)

    + Attributes (object)
        + employee_id: `b5094b3f-bb7a-0391-b01b-e709773f3509` (string, required)
        + project_id: `082e6289-30c5-45ad-bcd0-190b02d21e81` (string, optional)
        + internal_hourly_cost (Money, required)

+ Response 204 (application/json)
